WEBVTT

00:06.006 --> 00:08.600
Gentlemen, behold.

00:08.675 --> 00:11.439
The thermostat.

00:13.446 --> 00:14.504
That's been there.

00:14.581 --> 00:18.540
Observe as I adjust the heat.

00:20.000 --> 00:26.074
Advertise your product or brand here
